 image upload service.",[12,31,33],{"id":32},"imgur-prerequisites","Imgur prerequisites",[35,36,38],"h3",{"id":37},"create-an-imgur-album","Create an Imgur Album",[17,40,41],{},"First, learn how to create an Album — later, all uploaded images will be sorted into a specific Album.",[17,43,44],{},"Imgur used to let you create Albums directly, but they later hid the button and made it pretty hard to find. 80%+ of people can't find it, so follow these steps exactly.",[17,46,47],{},"Log in to Imgur. After login, click \"images\" in the user menu.",[17,49,50],{},[51,52],"img",{"alt":53,"src":54},"images","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172151.png",[17,56,57],{},"Find the \"All images\" dropdown — there's a \"New Album\". Click it.",[17,59,60],{},[51,61],{"alt":62,"src":63},"New Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172202.png",[17,65,66],{},"A modal pops up. Fill in the Album settings and click Save.",[17,68,69],{},[51,70],{"alt":71,"src":72},"Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172203.png",[17,74,75],{},"After creating, you'll see an empty page because we haven't added any images.",[17,77,78],{},[51,79],{"alt":71,"src":80},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.04.30.png",[17,82,83],{},"Album created.",[17,85,86],{},[87,88,89],"del",{},"Great Imgur UX.",[35,91,93],{"id":92},"get-the-album-id","Get the Album ID",[17,95,96],{},"We need the Album ID later to upload images. Click \"gallery profile\" in the user menu.",[17,98,99],{},[51,100],{"alt":101,"src":102},"gallery profile","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_08.png",[17,104,105],{},"Find \"Albums\" on the right.",[17,107,108],{},[51,109],{"alt":110,"src":111},"Albums","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_10.png",[17,113,114],{},"Click \"Posts\" → \"All\". The first one is the Album you just created.",[17,116,117],{},[51,118],{"alt":71,"src":119},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_11.png",[17,121,122],{},"Open the Album and check the URL — only the part in the red box is the Album ID. Remember it, we'll use it in Express.",[17,124,125],{},[51,126],{"alt":127,"src":128},"Album ID","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_13.png",[35,130,132],{"id":131},"register-an-imgur-application","Register an Imgur application",[17,134,135,136,140,141,144],{},"Now register an Imgur application — we need ",[137,138,139],"code",{},"client_id"," and ",[137,142,143],{},"client_secret"," for upload. Click the link below:",[17,146,147],{},[148,149,132],"a",{"href":150,"rel":151},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Faddclient",[152],"nofollow",[17,154,155],{},"You'll see this:",[17,157,158],{},[51,159],{"alt":160,"src":161},"Register","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.18.24.png",[17,163,164],{},"Required fields:",[166,167,168,177,185],"ul",{},[169,170,171,172],"li",{},"Application name\n",[166,173,174],{},[169,175,176],{},"Any name",[169,178,179,180],{},"Authorization type\n",[166,181,182],{},[169,183,184],{},"Choose \"OAuth 2 authorization without a callback URL\"",[169,186,187,188],{},"Email\n",[166,189,190],{},[169,191,192],{},"Contact info",[17,194,195,196,199],{},"PS: If you pick \"Anonymous usage without user authorization\", the \"Authorization callback URL\" needs to be ",[137,197,198],{},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com",".",[17,201,202],{},[51,203],{"alt":204,"src":205},"Application form","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_22.png",[17,207,208,209,140,211,213,214,216],{},"After applying, you'll see this. Save your ",[137,210,139],{},[137,212,143],{}," — especially ",[137,215,143],{},", don't lose it (if you do, you have to regenerate it).",[17,218,219],{},[51,220],{"alt":221,"src":222},"Application success","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_23.png",[17,224,225,226,228,229,234],{},"Application done. If you lose ",[137,227,143],{},", you can go to ",[148,230,233],{"href":231,"rel":232},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002Faccount\u002Fsettings\u002Fapps",[152],"Applications"," and click \"generate new secret\".",[17,236,237],{},[51,238],{"alt":239,"src":240},"Regenerate client_secret","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_26.png",[35,242,244],{"id":243},"get-an-imgur-refresh-token","Get an Imgur Refresh Token",[17,246,247,248,140,250,252],{},"We have ",[137,249,139],{},[137,251,143],{},". The last key piece is the Refresh Token. Imgur's Token has a time limit — to auto-refresh, you need a Refresh Token.",[17,254,255,256,259],{},"Getting it is unusual — replace ",[137,257,258],{},"${Client ID}"," in this URL with the one you just got:",[261,262,267],"pre",{"className":263,"code":264,"language":265,"meta":266,"style":266},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Fauthorize?client_id=${Client ID}&response_type=token\n","html","",[137,268,269],{"__ignoreMap":266},[270,271,274],"span",{"class":272,"line":273},"line",1,[270,275,264],{"class":276},"sMAXC",[17,278,279],{},"Paste it into your browser address bar and hit Enter.",[17,281,282],{},[51,283],{"alt":284,"src":285},"Address bar","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002F